### Request Forgot Password (Generate OTP)
POST /users/forgot-password HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:8888
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "arif.rahman@gmail.com"
}

### Verifikasi OTP
POST /users/forgot-password/verifikasi-otp HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:8888
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "arif.rahman@gmail.com",
    "code": 481272
}

### Change Password
PATCH /users/forgot-password/change HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:8888
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "arif2@mail.com",
    "newPassword": "1234",
    "confirmPassword": "1234"
}

